This software is pre-release and may contain defects or incomplete features. It is provided **"as is"** without warranties of any kind. Use is at your own risk.

To the maximum extent permitted by law, all implied warranties, including but not limited to merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, and non-infringement, are disclaimed.

Typeflows is not liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, or consequential damages resulting from use.

